  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      67.58,
      549.73,
      524.92,
      589.63
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy showers above 50 mm can be expected at some places in Sabaragamuwa and Central provinces and in the Galle and Matara districts.",
